, 2008, isolated from the decayed needles of 
<taxonomicName id="21A97FBBFFA6214BFBCCFD0DFB7C6EB1" box="[1047,1231,734,760]" class="Pinopsida" family="Pinaceae" genus="Pinus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pinales" pageId="7" pageNumber="218" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="densiflora">
