.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E6160438FFA6214BFF53FC99FF626F2D" blockId="7.[136,1451,843,1049]" box="[136,209,843,868]" pageId="7" pageNumber="218">
<emphasis id="D4DDD82AFFA6214BFF53FC99FF626F2D" box="[136,209,843,868]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="218">Notes:</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E6160438FFA6214BFF53FCBDFACA6851" blockId="7.[136,1451,843,1049]" pageId="7" pageNumber="218">
